These are Puzzles for 1x4 Level 1

.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-1-1::.
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: snowboarding, handball, golf, rowing
1. the person who's sport is snowboarding is on the left of the person who's sport is rowing##1
2. the person who's sport is handball is on the right of the person who's sport is golf##1
3. the person who's sport is snowboarding is on the right of the person who's sport is handball##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |  1  |    2    |    3    |  4   |
| Sport   | golf | handball | snowboarding | rowing |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-1-2::.
The people have 4 different jobs:  dancer, scientist, chef, software-developer
1. the software-developer is on the far right##1
2. the dancer is on the far left##1
3. the chef is on the right of the dancer##1

.:: Answer ::.
|       |  1   |   2   |     3      |   4    |
| Job   | dancer | chef | scientist | software-developer |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-1-3::.
There 4 different types of food: grapefruit, grapes, plum, lettuce
1. the person eating plum is on the left of the person eating grapefruit##1
2. the person eating grapes is on the left of the person eating lettuce##1
3. the person eating grapes is on the right of the person eating grapefruit##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |    1    |   2    |      3      |       4       |
| Food   | plum | grapefruit | grapes | lettuce |

