.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-1-4::.
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: drama, spy, comedy, musical
1. the person watching comedy movies is on the far left##1
2. the person watching musical movies is on the far right##1
3. the person watching spy movies is on the left of the person watching musical movies##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |   1    |  2   |    3    |  4  |
| Movie-Genre   | comedy | drama | spy | musical |

