.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-1-17::.
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: february, march, september, october
1. the person who's birthday is in march is on the left of the person who's birthday is in february##1
2. the person who's birthday is in october is on the left of the person who's birthday is in march##1
3. the person who's birthday is in september is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1   |  2   |    3    |  4   |
| Birthday   | october | march | february | september |

